title: WebOffice_coin
author: WebOffice_coin
content: WebOfficeWhat we have to do: Assist centralized network to complete decentralization.We're trying to put centralized data on a blockchain.Reward miners who mine on the test net and will be redeemed at 10/2.5 when the main net goes live.Five percent of the coin is the airdrop reward.-------------------------------------------Maximum Supply:  25,000,000 (WO)Block Time: 1 minuteBlock reward: 10 (WO)-------------------------------------------Website: https://weboffice.eu.org/Pool: https://weboffice.eu.org/web/#/poolBlockchain Explorer: https://weboffice.eu.org/web/#/explorerWallet: https://weboffice.eu.org/web/#/walletAirdrop: https://weboffice.eu.org/web/#/airdrop

What we aim to do is to package important data that we don't want to be tampered with into blocks, achieving decentralization for certain centralized data. In the future, we will release a complete desktop blockchain wallet. If you don't trust us at the moment, you can continue to follow us for a while. It is not the optimal time for coin mining at the moment.
